org.batfish.datamodel.questions

Class OspfPropertySpecifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.questions.PropertySpecifier
      • org.batfish.datamodel.questions.OspfPropertySpecifier

  • public class OspfPropertySpecifier
extends PropertySpecifier
    Enables specification a set of Ospf process properties.

    Example specifiers:

    • max-metric-summary-links -> gets the process's corresponding value
    • max-metric-.* -> gets all properties that start with 'max-metric-'
